reviewText: The movie is exactly what I remembered. I bought this DVD because of a fond memory. I wasn't expecting much with the movie because I had already seen it. It is nothing like the first Meatballs so if your thinking about purchasing this to satisfy a hunger for more after watching the first one you may be disappointed. Nostalgia got me again :)
